	- L2 CAT updated to operate on a per cluster/L2 ID basis
	- Support for MBA
2. SNMP
	- Added CMT support to Net-SNMP sub-agent
3. PQoS Utility
	- L2 CAT updated to operate on a per cluster/L2 ID basis
	- Support for MBA
4. rdtset Utility
	- L2 CAT updated to operate on a per cluster/L2 ID basis
	- Support of MBA

